<h1 id="conversation">Conversation</h1>
<p>Do multiple say and portrait commands in a single block of text. Format is: [character] [portrait] [stage position] [hide] [&lt;&lt;&lt; | &gt;&gt;&gt;] [clear | noclear] [wait | nowait] [fade | nofade] [: Story text]</p>
<p>Defined in Fungus.Conversation</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Property</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>Wait For Seconds</td>
<td>Fungus.FloatData</td>
<td>a wait for seconds added to each item of the conversation.</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h1 id="menu">Menu</h1>
<p>Displays a button in a multiple choice menu</p>
